author: weaver
msg: FileSystemPAM now continues to remove a web application directory even if unregister fails.
There have been SO many times when I needed this and undeploy fails.
PortletApplicationManager fails to undeploy with FileSystemPAM because it does not implement
Lifecycle.  Removed the lifecycle check, now everything works fine.
